description: Demolition of existing buildings and redevelopment of the site to provide new buildings ranging from 2 to 19 storeys in height comprising 510 residential units (use class C3), including 15% (76 units) affordable housing; 1,352sq.m of flexible commercial floorspace (use classes A1/A2/A3/B1/D1/D2) and 1,122sq.m of community use floorspace (use class D1), together with ground floor car parking, public realm and landscaping.
